dcterms:creator: Alex Krizhevsky
Geoffrey Hinton
dcterms:description: Cifar-10 is a natural image dataset including 60,000 colour images (32×32×3) with 10 classes such as airplane, bird and dog, etc. Each category consists of 5,000 training images and 1,000 ones for testing.
dcterms:title: Cifar-10

dcterms:creator: Alex Krizhevsky
Geoffrey Hinton
dcterms:description: Cifar-100 is a dataset that is similar to Cifar-10 but includes 100 fine-grained categories. It contains the same images as Cifar-10 but further divided into more specific classes.
dcterms:title: Cifar-100

dcterms:creator: Jia Deng

dcterms:description: STL-10 is a smaller dataset from ImageNet and involves 10 categories where each one includes 500 training samples and 800 test ones. It also has 100,000 images belonging to multiple unknown classes.
dcterms:title: STL-10
